Reasoning: The paper deals with the classification of misinformation on social networks, which involves analyzing the propagation of content. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Computation and Language (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), or Sound (cs.SD). However, since the paper focuses on the structural properties of content propagation cascades, it is more likely to belong to cs.SI or cs.CL.
